&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Staff Nurse - Medical Receiving Unit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a Band 5 registered nurse to work within the Medical Receiving Unit. MRU is a busy and friendly unit with a high turnover of patients both ambulatory and acutely unwell.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are recruiting an enthusiastic and highly motivated nurse who is ready for a new challenge in their career. We require staff to provide high quality care to all our patients. In return we provide a supportive environment, full induction and preceptorship with many opportunities to develop your skills and knowledge.&lt;/p&gt;
